### The Bottom Line

**Yes, there's a real product here.** The core concept — a persistent, async, voice-enabled AI workstation with workflow skills and human approval checkpoints — is commercially interesting and not well-served by existing tools.

**The path:** ~3-4 months of focused work to swap out the CLI dependency, add proper auth, and properly package it. The UI is already excellent. The architecture just needs the implementation-layer swaps.

